::Primal Prime::

    His sense of the object was growing stronger, he figured just a few 
corners and he would be there. Suddenly he blacked out. He had another vision.
    In this one someone was lying on a table. The person was dying. He handed 
something that looked very familiar to him. It slipped as the bot died. A bot 
that looked very similar to the bot known as Hot Rod grabbed it. A light 
shined from it and Hot Rod gave it to another bot.
